name: Sulliden Mining Capital Inc.
longDescription: Sulliden Mining Capital Inc is focused on generating value through the acquisition and development of quality mining projects in the Americas, in addition to identifying opportunities across industries for active investments. It holds mineral exploration interests in the East Sullivan property in Quebec and various investments in public and private entities.
